# WeChat → mygear-wiki

When the user pastes an `mp.weixin.qq.com` link (alone or with「处理这篇到 mygear-wiki」):

1. Read and follow the project skill: `.cursor/skills/wechat-to-wiki/SKILL.md`
2. Execute end-to-end without waiting for section / filename / nav title unless fetch fails
3. Never show source in the page body; always store `source_url` in YAML frontmatter + `sources.yaml`
4. Do not commit or push unless explicitly asked

Local preview base: `http://127.0.0.1:8000/mygear-wiki/`
